---
title: Pan-Fried Turkey Scallopini with Sweet Potato Mash and Savoury Gravy
description: Celebrate the holiday season with delicious turkey and some of our favourite trimmings! Sweet potato mash and roasted broccoli are the perfect sides for this delightful dinner.
